n.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 郁D都成千萬起跳"},{"pid":"c62c011857bd9ab32c99738898ec9f8e24dcc714","tid":185421,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T05:02:58.000Z","msg":"<strong>【超人答問會】李嘉誠哽咽：香港無理想，只顧炒樓、賺多啲、樓起高啲</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2017-03-22</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">其後，李嘉誠首度在眾人、鏡頭面前哽咽，聲音沙咳重申：「我愛香港，希望再見到本地一直引以為傲的香港&hellip;&hellip;」李嘉誠說畢有點眼紅、眼鏡起霧，哽咽斷續稱，「今日香港&hellip;&hellip;GDP&hellip;&hellip;得返2%」，<strong>又指自己自40年代已到香港，自己是香港人，香港以往有活力，但今日只見大家顧住「炒樓、賺多啲、樓起高啲」，已經無理想。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n他其後否認自己喊，「只係有少少傷風，少少感冒」。長和發言人於會後澄清，主席李嘉誠今日在業績會上「只是有少少傷風」，答問題時並沒有哽咽。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170322&amp;guid=56464314&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170322%26guid%3D56464314%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=794f1771\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170322%26guid%3D56464314%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&h=ced04f7a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170322&amp;guid=56464314&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"97fa011cd586bd9de3f55a3faea70db65bf68951","tid":185421,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T05:04:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果共產黨出黎話清算呢d人渣<br />\n同埋會起超多公屋個個香港家庭都有得住，仲要大單位<br />\n條件係要支持共產黨施政<br />\n你地肯唔肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果俾屋我住<br />\n要我屠殺100萬香港人都照做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eef3657d1df2c37873aab490d1e24e26f16aea1","tid":185421,"uid":43721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T05:07:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果共產黨出